{"tid":1145401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［活著就無悔地做個你愛的你］一人一篇致十年後的你","createTime":"2019-05-08T16:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T15:18:04.000Z","uid":25621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a574f5311f59f0ba6d6306fcae7fb7467406bfff","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"致十年後的我<br />\n<br />\n可能你而家睇返依篇野嘅時候 人生都走到三分一 但可能有好多事情都未達預期目標 都希望你努力做好自己。<br />\n行你要行嘅路，唔好盲目跟從人地嘅路 <br />\n保持著年輕時候嘅想法。人生最緊要無悔、活得開心精彩<br />\n錢樓車都係身外物，身邊愛你嘅人先係你值得保護嘅野<br />\n希望你可以名留青史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9/5/2019<br />\n十年前的你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們，希望大家都可以留低啲說話比十年後嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都深信連登會有十年命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4c0a5bd597d9fe547b1aed1e40cb57dbfb09be","tid":1145401,"uid":113373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捍衛香港 終局之戰<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d6727f9edcf06f303bdb446b43f911beccc2107","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"大家唔洗怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2505d2e4c55bb4f1239651d00004d5a24a763759","tid":1145401,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"想同10年前嘅自己講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58d172c572af9819c962fcccf290097de38d4d5","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2505d2e4c55bb4f1239651d00004d5a24a763759","tid":1145401,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"想同10年前嘅自己講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"講比十年後嘅自己聽 令十年後嘅你唔會再後悔"},{"pid":"205173fc38883dcd323886517f19af071c93c4e0","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T21:33:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07435966a34a1bbe8872b50bf5069f7ac210a8c5","tid":1145401,"uid":236414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T21:45:56.000Z","msg":"致十年後的我<br />\n要保持初心"},{"pid":"abcd7053b3b02c826f778b16ec6ce85ae4a5501a","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac63b3182e2857db53210a1a9b5fad2ea871ba7","tid":1145401,"uid":25621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}